modShortDescription: Gopher made a 7DTD mod where you can craft an Ear of Super Corn, or rather, a mutated normal Ear of Corn, since he assume that's what Super Corn is.
modDescription:
Gopher thought he would make a 7DTD mod where you can craft an Ear of Super Corn, or rather, a mutated normal Ear of Corn, since he assume that’s what Super Corn is. He also did this seeing as you can’t get Super Corn on Random Gen normally.

**[Download](https://github.com/GopherMods/7DTDMods/raw/master/CraftableSuperCorn.zip)**

The forum topic of the mod is [here](https://community.7daystodie.com/topic/17309-gophers-modlets-not-an-all-in-one-pack/).

**Credits:** [Gopher](https://7daystodiemods.com/tag/gopher/)
